'''Dando''' was a [[Corporal/Legends|corporal]] in the [[Imperial Army/Legends|Imperial Army]] who oversaw a lighthouse beacon on the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Empire's]] [[Prison/Legends|penal colony]] on [[Mika (planetoid)|Jellyfish Cove]]. He was presumably killed by [[Bara (Mikan)|Bara]], a native [[Mikan]] who later used his uniform to walk in the daylight. Despite being referred to in passing as 'he' by [[Garve]], a [[Mercenary/Legends|mercenary]] later hired to oversee the beacon, Dando's uniform and [[Body glove/Legends|bodyglove]] fit Bara well when the [[Changeling/Legends|shapeshifter]] took the form of a [[Gender/Legends|female]] [[Humanoid/Legends|humanoid]].

